d324e9f?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU =
] and Claude [ https://substack.com/redirect/93472940-6c0c-495b-8998-33cfff=
7f2023?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]=
 for editing!
That=E2=80=99s all for today. We=E2=80=99ll be back in your inbox with a We=
ekly Dose on Friday.
Thanks for reading,
Packy

