n: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The problem isn&#8217;t slop itself. Slop on its own =
is </span><em>fine.</em><span> The internet is a big place, and people shou=
ld be free to produce whatever shitty things they want to produce on their =
low-traffic websites and low-follower-count social media accounts.&#160;</s=
pan></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 2=
6px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The problem is the fact that we have to see=
 it, that it </span><em>works.</em><span>&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color=
: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"=
