=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">The deployment phase is impactful and boring and profitable&#8230=
; until it isn&#8217;t.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Because the Deployment P=
