 contains its own self-destruct codes. When things get predictable, the peo=
ple yearn for something new and different.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(=
54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The g=
ood news is that every once in a while, a new paradigm comes around that bu=
